#               canonical CLI tool for publishing static websites to the
#               Nostr nsite (NIP-34128) static-website protocol on top
#               of blossom-server blob storage.  The "Vercel / Netlify /
#               GitHub Pages for the decentralized Nostr web" — uploads
#               a folder of HTML / CSS / JS / images to one or more
#               blossom servers, then publishes NIP-34128 kind:34128
#               website-content events to Nostr relays that map URL
#               paths to blossom SHA-256 hashes, addressable from any
#               nsite-aware gateway as `https://<npub>.nsite.lol/<path>`
#               or `https://npub.cash/.../<path>`.
#               TS-Node=166 CLOSING leg of Axis 111 (Nostr protocol) at
#               1/1/1 with TRIPLE-166 landmark + 104th axis closed via
#               the canonical TS/JS Nostr SDK `nostr-tools` (+ NDK
#               `@nostr-dev-kit/ndk`).
