#   canonical TS/JS Nostr SDK — the **JavaScript reference
#   implementation of the Nostr protocol**, authored and
#   maintained by **fiatjaf** (Vítor Pamplona, the inventor of
#   Nostr, who also maintains the canonical Go SDK
#   nbd-wtf/go-nostr under the same nbd-wtf umbrella).  Every
